OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA grey and cloudy start with
OL,6,Flow cloud shrouding the hills. Rain
OL,7,Fwill move into Cumbria through the
OL,8,Fmorning, turning persistent over the
OL,9,Fhills, before easing in the afternoon.
OL,10,FSome brighter spells are possible in
OL,11,Fthe south during the afternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloudy with some outbreaks of
OL,14,Frain across northern parts of the
OL,15,Fregion this evening. Low cloud, mist
OL,16,Fand murk moving into the coast.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FA grey start, but cloud slowly
OL,19,Flifting through the day. Some warm
OL,20,Fbrighter glimmers are possible at
OL,21,Ftimes, particularly in the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
