OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FTurning increasingly bright through
OL,7,Fthe outlook with some warm sunny
OL,8,Fspells. However, cloud will spill in
OL,9,Fat times, particularly across the
OL,10,Fnorth. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
